searchableProductInfo.editorsNotes: Jimmy Choo's coveted carryalls are loved for their scene-stealing power, and this animal-print calf hair shoulder bag is a fine example of the label's glamorous aesthetic. Detailed with super luxe gold-tone chains and opulent studs, this mini design will make the perfect punctuation point to after-dark looks. Tote yours with a tuxedo jacket and leather pants for a cool approach to cocktail dressing.Shown here with: Gucci jacket and leggings, Kain tank, Oscar de la Renta ring, Valentino shoes.
